(14,	'Valerio Mello',	'mellovalerio@gmail.com',	'Contact',	'Dear Dimitris Lyacos, i write to you from  Milano, Italia. Nice to meet you. I am poet and writer, i will write about Poena Damni on the italian newspaper Studi Cattolici which i work with. I am also been  represented  by Edelweiss Literary Agency (Mr Carnevale published my last book \'Rive\' of poetry in Italia). So it is  very happy to write to you and want say congratulazionts for your work...i hope to meet you too. And i hope we will keep in touch.',	'2022-11-09 13:12:35',	'2022-11-09 13:12:35'),
