(16,	'Augusto',	'augustoolivella@yahoo.com.ar',	'Contact',	'Hi, my name is Augusto Olivella. I\'m from Buenos Aires, Argentina, and i´m very interested in buy the trilogy that you wrote. Unfortunaly i can´t find it in any library or book shop of my country. That´s is way i want to know if there is some traductión to the spanish, and, if it don´t, maybe you can tell me the way to buy a copy in english. Thank you.',	'2023-01-09 01:54:26',	'2023-01-09 01:54:26'),
