(74,	'Evening with an author',	'evening-with-an-author',	'American Library in Paris',	'<p>A conversation with Dimitris Lyacos, Vanessa Onwuemezi, and Nafkote Tamirat at the American Library in Paris. Filmed on 13/03/2024 with a live audience both in person and on Zoom.&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nclhsGfc5i8&amp;t=264s\" target=\"_BLANK\">youTube Link</a><br></p><p>Join us for an exchange between two contemporary writers: Dimitris Lyacos, author of the highly-esteemed Poena Damni trilogy and Vanessa Onwuemezi, Scholar of Note at the American Library in Paris. </p>',	'Paris',	'France',	'2024-03-19 00:00:00',	'19:30',	'2024-03-19 00:00:00',	'22:00',	'2024-02-13 11:20:20',	'2024-05-30 14:14:59'),
